  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的数据流转图。场景是这样的：有两台边缘计算节点，它们通过MQTT Broker中转数据，而且Broker之间还要做级联。整体是个链式结构，从左到右流动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，链式结构。让我确认一下：第一台边缘节点发送数据到第一个Broker，然后这个Broker转发到第二台边缘节点？还是Broker之间直接互联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是Broker之间级联。具体流程是：边缘节点A → Broker 1 → 边缘节点B → Broker 2 → Broker 3。最后那个Broker 3是汇聚层，负责把数据送上云端。这样总共是5个节点连成一条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，5个节点链式连接，方向从左到右。我标记为A到E，其中A、C是边缘节点，B、D、E是MQTT Broker。E作为汇聚终点。这个理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。不过E虽然是终点，但它本质上还是Broker，和B、D同类型。只是在这个流程里它不再向下转发而已。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了，我来绘制。用LR布局，A连B，B连C，C连D，D连E。A和C标注为工业边缘节点，B、D、E标注为工业MQTT Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚发现个细节。B和D都是Broker，但B是接收边缘节点数据的接入层Broker，D是转发给汇聚层E的转发层Broker。虽然类型一样，但位置不同，图上能体现出这个层级感吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "链式LR布局本身就有顺序感，从左到右自然形成接入层→边缘节点→转发层→汇聚层的层级。B在最左的Broker位置，E在最右终点，这个空间位置应该能表达层级差异。需要额外标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "空间位置够了，不用额外标注，保持简洁。不过我想确认一下连线方式，都是单向箭头对吧？数据只从左往右流，没有回流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，全部单向连接：A→B→C→D→E。没有反向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个点，E作为汇聚Broker，后面其实还要连云端，但那个不在我们这张图的范围里。E就作为当前图的终点，没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "没问题，E作为当前链式结构的终点，保持开放感暗示后续还有连接。图已经完成了：两台工业边缘节点、三台工业MQTT Broker，五级串联，单向数据流。我最终确认一下结构——A边缘节点→B接入Broker→C边缘节点→D转发Broker→E汇聚Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
